274C9842.VoiceDir19.9118B: Considering this revelation from Neyrelle. Giving in, but not exactly happy about it. She's still concerned of putting a child in harm's way.

294A5229.Line27.6DE47: We think Elias made a pact with the swamp to become immortal. Taissa said you could help--

3114EE91.VoiceDir9.9118B: Cryptic. Making up her mind for the last part of the line--she doesn't want to send a child to her death.

47C8302F.Line31.9118B: There are many paths to reach it, but the nearest is in Yngovani.

67F2F814.Line45.9118B: If this Elias made a pact, it was with the Tree of Whispers.

B82923E1.VoiceDir45.9118B: Considering this revelation from Neyrelle. Giving in, but not exactly happy about it. She's still concerned of putting a child in harm's way.

C20B8864.Line9.9118B: One of you will. That’s the way it always ends. Go back where you came from. I won’t have a child’s blood on my hands.

C3584156.Line29.9118B: Taissa? Only she would be coldhearted enough to send a child to die out here.

CDFE7E92.Line43.9118B: A sacred incense is kept in the temple there. Retrieve it, and your path to the Tree begins.

DFA57A1F.VoiceDir25.9118B: Dissuading. Timue is fated to direct people toward the Tree, but she knows it often ends in death for these people. It's her fate--but she doesn't necessarily enjoy it.

E1A33406.Line33.6DE47: I saw my mother possessed by Lilith. Driven so mad it killed her. I’m not a child anymore.
